Module jtrim.image.query
Package org.jtrim2.image.async

Class IIOReadProgressAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.jtrim2.image.async.IIOReadProgressAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventListener, IIOReadProgressListener
public class IIOReadProgressAdapter extends Object implements IIOReadProgressListener
Defines a convenient base class for IIOReadProgressListener implementations when you only want to implement some of its methods.

All the implemented methods of IIOReadProgressAdapter does nothing but return immediately and subclasses may override them for their purpose.

Thread safety

Since the methods of IIOReadProgressAdapter does nothing, they are safe to be accessed from multiple threads. Subclasses of IIOReadProgressAdapter are not required to be safe to be accessed by multiple threads concurrently.

Synchronization transparency

Since the methods of IIOReadProgressAdapter does nothing, they are synchronization transparent. As a listener interface, subclasses of IIOReadProgressAdapter are not required to be synchronization transparent but should return reasonably fast.
